desc:
Copyright (c) 2025 Tencent. All rights reserved.
Module:   BarrageStore @ AtomicXCore
Function: Barrage related interfaces, managing barrage sending, barrage state synchronization, and barrage event listening operations in live rooms/voice chat rooms.

name: Barrage
desc: Barrage data model, containing complete attribute information of a single barrage.

name: businessID
desc: Business identifier ID of custom type barrage, used to distinguish custom barrages in different business scenarios.

name: data
desc: Specific data content of custom type barrage (usually a JSON format string), valid when messageType{@link BarrageType} is CUSTOM.

name: extensionInfo
desc: Barrage extension information, customizable fields (such as display style, priority, etc.). Valid when messageType {@link BarrageType} is TEXT.

name: liveID
desc: The unique identifier ID of the live room/voice chat room to which the barrage belongs.

name: messageType
desc: Barrage message type (text or custom). {@link BarrageType}

name: sender
desc: User information of the barrage sender (such as user ID, nickname, avatar, etc.). {@link $LiveUserInfo$}

name: sequence
desc: Unique sequence ID of the barrage message, used for message sorting and deduplication.

name: textContent
desc: Message content of text type barrage, i.e., the text content of the barrage.

name: timestampInSecond
desc: Barrage sending timestamp (unit: seconds), used to display the sending time order.

name: BarrageState
desc: Barrage state, managing the barrage data state of the current room.

name: messageList
desc: Barrage message list of the current room, supporting real-time updates and subscription listening. {@link Barrage}

name: appendLocalTip
desc: Add local tip message (add tip or operation feedback message locally, visible only to the current client).

name: barrageState
desc: Barrage state subscription of the current room, containing barrage message list and other information. By subscribing to this state, you can get real-time updates of barrage data in the room. {@link BarrageState}

name: create
desc: Barrage management core class, used to handle barrage related business logic in live rooms/voice chat rooms.

name: BarrageType
desc: Barrage type enumeration, used to distinguish different types of barrage messages.

name: values
desc: A constant List of the values in this enum, in order of their declaration.
